  EffectDiscription_ENG: When you trash this card in your hand using one of your
    effects, you may place it under 1 of your purple Digimon at the bottom of its
    digivolution cards.[When Attacking] You may trash 1 card in your hand to have
    this Digimon get +3000 DP for the turn.
